      "span_text": "For drug efficacy studies using an organoid-derived murine model of pancreatic cancer, spherical, duct-like organoids were derived and cultured in Matrigel and defined media as previously described from pancreatic ductal adenocarcinoma (PDAC) occurring in Kras LSL-G12D/+; Trp53 fl/+; CHC (untargeted collagen homing cassette); RIK (Rosa26-LSL-rtTa3-IRES-Kate2); p48Cre mice (GEMM-KPC fl/+ ) generated via the PDAC-GEMM-ESC approach"
